+/**
+ * DIV_ROUND_UP_NO_OVERFLOW - divide two numbers and always round up
+ * @n: numerator / dividend
+ * @d: denominator / divisor
+ *
+ * This functions does the same as DIV_ROUND_UP, but internally uses a
